33
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:37,440
The supply fan is on the 
far right of the schematic.

34
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:41,280
It is an electromechanical system that 
powers the air to expel it from the  

35
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:44,400
AHU to the ducts that distribute 
the air throughout the library.

